{"tid":2478599,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《路透》︰中國10年一度的人口普查預期將呈現年輕人口比例的下滑","createTime":"2021-04-07T07:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T08:26:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"19cf5e5055c9849d3d65222905fb26780e7d2ec0","tid":2478599,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:33:31.000Z","msg":"《路透》報導，中國10年一度的人口普查預期將會呈現出年輕人口比例的下滑，原因在於生活成本昂貴，加上都市配偶不想要有孩子，中國可能會進一步人口緊縮。報導指出，中國執政者面臨壓力，要提出獎勵生育計畫，遏止出生率下降，如果沒有有效措施，這個全世界人口最多的國家將會進入不可逆的人口下滑斜坡。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，對於近來即將釋出的普查報告，外界認為中國老年人口占比將會上升，年輕人口占比則會下降，上一次的人口普查顯示，14歲以下人口占比從2000年的22.89%降至16.6%，這是一胎化政策所遺留下的結果，此一趨勢將會降低中國的勞動人口，進一步壓低生育率，因為勞動人口要負擔起照顧老年人口的壓力。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，中國官媒預估人口將會在未來幾年持續減少，假如平均每位女性生育率降至1.5個孩子以下，學者認為中國將無法脫離生育率陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3492124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3492124&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=c1469d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3492124&h=029d122e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3492124</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-society-census/chinas-census-could-point-to-a-looming-demographic-slide-idUSKBN2BU0DI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-society-census%2Fchinas-census-could-point-to-a-looming-demographic-slide-idUSKBN2BU0DI&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtG%2FWCCUevL1oElw8znUqpaw%3D&h=444d8e79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Fus-china-society-census%2Fchinas-census-could-point-to-a-looming-demographic-slide-idUSKBN2BU0DI&h=eca48a7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-society-census/chinas-census-could-point-to-a-looming-demographic-slide-idUSKBN2BU0DI</a>"},{"pid":"3800ce7d504